OL,3,CLabour MP with disabled son says he
OL,4,Cwon't vote for benefits changes
OL,6,F"Nobody in North Somerset put me here
OL,7,Fjust to rubber stamp and approve
OL,8,Flegislation," Al-Hassan said.
OL,10,F"They want me to read it, understand
OL,11,Fit, and vote on what I think is right.
OL,12,FThey want me to make a call on what I
OL,13,Fthink would be best for North Somerset.
OL,15,F"It is tough sometimes to stand up and
OL,16,Fsay, 'actually, I disagree.'"
