OL,3,CLabour MP with disabled son says he
OL,4,Cwon't vote for benefits changes
OL,6,FIn a bid to ease growing discontent,
OL,7,Fthe government said PIP recipients who
OL,8,Fwill lose the benefit would get a 13-
OL,9,Fweek extension to help ease the
OL,10,Ftransition.
OL,12,F"From the government's own impact
OL,13,Fassessment, it's going to bring about
OL,14,F250,000 disabled people into poverty
OL,15,Fand about 50,000 children," Al-Hassan
OL,16,Fadded.
